{"data":[{"name":"96:1","price":"1. Bacalah dengan (menyebut) nama Tuhanmu yang menciptakan.","arabic":"ٱقۡرَأۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6107,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:2","price":"2. Dia telah menciptakan manusia dari segumpal darah.","arabic":"خَلَقَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مِنۡ عَلَقٍ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6108,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:3","price":"3. Bacalah, dan Tuhanmulah Yang Mahamulia.","arabic":"ٱقۡرَأۡ وَرَبُّكَ ٱلۡأَكۡرَمُ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6109,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:4","price":"4. Yang mengajar (manusia) dengan pena.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي عَلَّمَ بِٱلۡقَلَمِ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6110,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:5","price":"5. Dia mengajarkan manusia apa yang tidak diketahuinya.","arabic":"عَلَّمَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مَا لَمۡ يَعۡلَمۡ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6111,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:6","price":"6. Sekali-kali tidak! Sungguh, manusia itu benar-benar melampaui batas,","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ لَيَطۡغَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6112,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:7","price":"7. Apabila melihat dirinya serba cukup.","arabic":"أَن رَّءَاهُ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6113,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:8","price":"8. Sungguh, hanya kepada Tuhanmulah tempat kembali(mu).","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ ٱلرُّجۡعَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6114,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:9","price":"9. Bagaimana pendapatmu tentang orang yang melarang?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يَنۡهَىٰ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6115,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:10","price":"10. Seorang hamba ketika dia melaksanakan salat.*(918)","arabic":"عَبۡدًا إِذَا صَلَّىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6116,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*918). Yang melarang adalah Abu Jahal dan yang dilarang ialah Rasulullah. Tetapi usaha ini tidak berhasil karena Abu Jahal melihat sesuatu yang menakutkannya. Setelah Rasulullah selesai salat, disampaikannya berita itu kepada Rasulullah. Kemudian Rasulullah mengatakan, “Kalau Abu Jahal berbuat demikian, niscaya dia akan dibinasakan oleh malaikat.”","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:11","price":"11. Bagaimana pendapatmu jika dia (yang dilarang salat itu) berada di atas kebenaran (petunjuk),","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ إِن كَانَ عَلَى ٱلۡهُدَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6117,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:12","price":"12. atau dia menyuruh bertakwa (kepada Allah)?","arabic":"أَوۡ أَمَرَ بِٱلتَّقۡوَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6118,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:13","price":"13. Bagaimana pendapatmu jika dia (yang melarang) itu mendustakan dan berpaling?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ إِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6119,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:14","price":"14. Tidakkah dia mengetahui bahwa sesungguhnya Allah melihat (segala perbuatannya)?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَعۡلَم بِأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ يَرَىٰ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6120,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:15","price":"15. Sekali-kali tidak! Sungguh, jika dia tidak berhenti (berbuat demikian) niscaya Kami tarik ubun-ubunnya (ke dalam neraka),","arabic":"كَلَّا لَئِن لَّمۡ يَنتَهِ لَنَسۡفَعَۢا بِٱلنَّاصِيَةِ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6121,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:16","price":"16. (yaitu) ubun-ubun orang yang mendustakan dan durhaka.","arabic":"نَاصِيَةٖ كَٰذِبَةٍ خَاطِئَةٖ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6122,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:17","price":"17. Maka biarlah dia memanggil golongannya (untuk menolongnya),","arabic":"فَلۡيَدۡعُ نَادِيَهُۥ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6123,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:18","price":"18. Kelak Kami akan memanggil Malaikat Zabaniyah (penyiksa orang-orang yang berdosa).","arabic":"سَنَدۡعُ ٱلزَّبَانِيَةَ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6124,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"96:19","price":"19. Sekali-kali tidak! Janganlah kamu patuh kepadanya; dan sujudlah serta dekatkanlah (dirimu kepada Allah).","arabic":"كَلَّا لَا تُطِعۡهُ وَٱسۡجُدۡۤ وَٱقۡتَرِب۩","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6125,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq","Chapter Al-Alaq","Alaq","Surah Alaq","Chapter Alaq","Al Alaq","Surah Al Alaq","Chapter Al Alaq","Surah 96","Chapter 96","The Clot","العلق"]}